text: haey chea karpit nasa banda anakneasar moun anak ka trauv ban ke bdeseth der bo nde puokke ban atthmot champoh avei del trauv ban ke bdeseth ning trauv ban ke thveutoukkh bok me n nhnoh rhaut tealte chomnuoy robsa yeung ban towdl puokke daoy kmean karophlasabdaur peaky pech teanglay robsa a l laoh noh laey . haey damnoeng muoy chamnuon robsa banda anakneasar pitchea ban mokadl anak
